<div class="title">Addicted to My Meds</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=OKComputer&Exact=1">OKComputer</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; OKComputer. "Addicted to My Meds: An Experience with Amphetamines (Adderall) (exp22122)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 7, 2007. erowid.org/exp/22122</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
